Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.05,0:00:06.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The S Class Wizard Advancement \NExam has finally begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:09.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The first test is to choose a battle route,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:12.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and win your way through...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.09,0:00:14.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Natsu's opponent was \NGildarts, right off the bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:18.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was tough going, but that's \N'cause I held back a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:20.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice try there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:56.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Tenroujima.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:02:00.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it's okay for \Nus to follow them there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:03.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? We're just going to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.38,0:02:05.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Worried about Wendy, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.07,0:02:10.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I was so \Ndead-set against it, she...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:16.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:26.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened a week ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:38.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:43.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:47.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mest. I was Mystogan's disciple.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:49.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystogan's disciple?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:53.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard quite a lot \Nabout you from Mystogan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:56.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:58.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know what the snow tastes like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.13,0:02:59.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:01.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:02.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:04.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you lend me a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:07.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that any attitude to \Nhave when asking favors?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:13.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Apologies... When I want to know something,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:16.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a tendency to get obsessed about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:22.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy... With your power, I can get to \Nknow the world of an S Class wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:25.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, lend me your aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:28.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, someone like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:30.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.28,0:03:33.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:37.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know what the \Nriver is like in winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:39.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go along with this \Nweirdo! Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:42.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But he doesn't seem like a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:43.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he does!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:51.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to return all the \Nkindness Mystogan showed me at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:55.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved Edolas! That's plenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:59.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was more just \Nhow things turned out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:02.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't about how I felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:04.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! Just don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.52,0:04:11.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And in the end, she decided to \Nhelp Mest in Mystogan's stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.76,0:04:15.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why you haven't \Nspoken this past week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:17.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a lot more stubborn than she looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:18.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:22.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care really about this Mest guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:26.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the exam as a whole I have \Na really bad feeling about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:29.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your power to see the future, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:32.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure... It's too \Nfragmented, so I can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:36.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm curious about this Mest fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.39,0:04:41.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystogan's disciple... It doesn't sit right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:50.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know. I want \Nto know your abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:52.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mest-san, they're going to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:05:01.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all the people, it's Mest and \NWendy we get to fight with...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:02.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't holding back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:05.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make... Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:08.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When did he....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:13.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Power... Power of the heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Sky Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:18.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Regulus, grant me the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:24.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some force, all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:27.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:50.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:52.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't gonna hold back, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:53.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate Secret Technique:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:56.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just Eating Pickled Plums!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:10.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even eating them, but just \Nwatching makes my mouth pucker up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.94,0:06:13.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this some kind of transmission magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:15.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:17.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Regulus at full brightness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:34.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elsewhere, the pair of Evergreen \Nand Elfman have engaged Mirajane.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:43.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She who strikes first wins! Stone Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:46.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I don't look you in the \Neyes, that magic doesn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,0:06:49.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And can you dodge these while looking away?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:51.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Machine Gun Leprechaun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:58.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Evergreen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:05.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Neechan... You're serious about this, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:19.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Full Body Take Over! Beast Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:31.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The finishing blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:32.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:36.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll blow the both of you away, Evergreen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:39.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you something \Nyou might want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:50.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mest-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:55.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize those \Nguys would be so strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:57.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sure they're strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:08:00.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I'm going to follow \Nin Mystogan's footsteps!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:02.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:05.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on, Gray, Loke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:08.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:11.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... We lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:13.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:17.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,While you were unconscious, Gray-san \Nand Loke-san went on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:24.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So this year's no good, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.51,0:08:26.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I wasn't any help...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.89,0:08:30.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I decided to \Ntry as hard as I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:38.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's okay. Anyway, you're not hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:40.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:49.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right on! We cleared the first test!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:52.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although if Natsu, for example, lost \Nagainst Fried in the first test,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:54.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd feel better about what's coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:58.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Cana might be a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.42,0:09:03.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be a fool. There's no such thing as \Nan easy path to becoming an S Class wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:08.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking we did \Nwell by beating Mest...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:12.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which... Was he always that weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:17.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting Wendy aside... I thought \Nhe was stronger before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:19.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that we've gotten stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:22.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:26.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have I fought with him before?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:30.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Memory loss now, too? \NLucy'll think that's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:36.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Mest said that he got \Npretty far in last year's exam...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:39.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he did...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.57,0:09:43.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He... Who was his partner last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:45.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who was it, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:49.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it? I can't remember at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:50.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither can I.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:54.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell something is hazy \Nabout my memories of Mest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:10:00.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true... It's like my memories \Nof Mest are broken off somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:07.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, Loke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:11.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you two would pass the first test!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:13.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:16.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were lucky and got the peaceful route.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:19.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky?! I didn't get to smack anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:23.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're the only ones \Nto pass the first exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:25.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:26.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:31.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:32.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:34.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.42,0:10:37.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, I think everyone is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:38.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:44.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now announce the results, to date.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:49.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana and Lucy defeated Fried and \NBickslow in battle, and passed through!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:51.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:56.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu and Happy managed to get past \NGildarts somehow, and passed through!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:58.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kiddin' me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:11:00.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:05.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Levy and Gajeel passed through the \Npeaceful route with good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:07.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sayin' I got good luck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:11.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray and Loke defeated Mest and \NWendy in battle, and passed through!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:14.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Juvia fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:16.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What, Gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:21.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia and Lisanna hit upon... her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:25.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That female knight who knows not \Nthe meaning of holding back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:28.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The End.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:30.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:35.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then all that's left is Elfman and Evergreen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:39.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we consider what's left, \Nthey must have taken the route...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:43.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirajane...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:45.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sucks to be them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.19,0:11:47.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I could still have won.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:49.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:54.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We beat Oneechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:56.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've passed through the first test!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:57.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:58.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you beat Mira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:03.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say... As a Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:06.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just say we managed to \Nfind an opening to slip through.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:08.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck did they do, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:13.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway... The teams that \Npassed the first test are:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:16.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu and Happy, Gray and Loke,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:19.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Levy and Gajeel, Cana and Lucy,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:21.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman and Evergreen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:23.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those five teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:27.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we will begin the second test!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:31.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, how long are you going to sulk?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:35.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Just thinking about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.59,0:12:39.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu is! Thinking about! Something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:42.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How little do you take him for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:44.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:49.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out there and become \Nan S Class wizard, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:55.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you, Gildarts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:13:02.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, Cana, Levy, Elfman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:05.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight and see just who'll \Nbecome an S Class wizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You, especially, I ain't gonna lose to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:10.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither will I.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:13.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As a Man, I will take on that challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:17.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gettin' fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:18.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:22.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make Cana S Class, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:25.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm fighting you, \NLucy, I won't hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:29.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep barkin', strays.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:31.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who would be Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:34.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman, get it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:37.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look good for those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:43.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, I will announce the details for the \Nsecond test of the S Class Wizard Advancement Exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.74,0:14:03.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The second test is searching for the grave \Nof Mavis, our founding Guild Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:05.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Founding Guild Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:07.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mavis's grave...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:10.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That sounds easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.15,0:14:11.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.11,0:14:13.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have only 6 hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.86,0:14:17.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear that? I said 6 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:20.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting at Mavis's grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:24.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Righto! Let's go, Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.68,0:14:26.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:29.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Around that time, Wendy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:35.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to stay like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:37.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:44.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Wendy... Do you know why this island \Nis called Fairy Tail's Holy Ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:50.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's where its founding \NGuild Master, Mavis, rests.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:53.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. But that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.29,0:14:58.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This island is usually hidden \Nby a powerful barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:15:02.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what magic you use, you \Nwouldn't be able to find it, I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.06,0:15:07.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's because there's more \Nhere than just Mavis's grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:16.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, a big secret relating to \NFairy Tail is hidden on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:18.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.76,0:15:20.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:24.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it? Want to explore?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:37.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Prince... I mean, Mystogan, tried to \Navoid contact with the people of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:45.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that he would put everyone to sleep \Nso as not to show his face in the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:50.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's difficult for me to think \Nhe'd take on a disciple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:51.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:57.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pretty out-there \Nhypothesis, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pretty place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:05.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:23.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Mest really a member of the guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:30.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:32.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:46.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This island is nuts...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:47.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I might die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:51.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To become S class, this ain't nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.33,0:16:52.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to put on a brave face!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:55.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here, Evergreen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.02,0:16:57.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Don't order me around!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:16:59.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.03,0:17:02.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the way of the exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:06.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad luck for the ones who \Nshowed up in front of Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:15.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job as always, Natsu. Let's move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:17.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait, Happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:21.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me where the grave \Nof the founding master is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:22.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's talking to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:24.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.47,0:17:24.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:27.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:32.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, having us search for a \Ngrave without even a hint...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.78,0:17:36.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This second test might be \Nharder than we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:41.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah... Wasn't this \Nisland shaped like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.19,0:17:42.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:44.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That top seem suspicious to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:45.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:50.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I knew partnering with \Nyou was the right choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:51.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To the top, Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:53.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.56,0:17:59.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the examiner's base on Tenroujima.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:03.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Elfman and Evergreen \Nare getting married?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:07.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And while I was still blanked \Nout, they landed some attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:08.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:13.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When's the wedding? And wait, \Nwhen did those two start...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:17.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I think it was just a \Nplan to throw me off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:19.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I have a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:21.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really just a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:25.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two? I don't really see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:29.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if they get married and have a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:40.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry, Mira... It's cute \Nthe way you imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.63,0:18:45.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elf-niichan and Evergreen... They're \Nkind of birds of a feather, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:47.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,K-K-Kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:50.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where's Fried?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.59,0:18:53.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They went back to the guild with Gildarts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.34,0:18:57.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast... I wish I \Ncould have seen him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:19:00.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, where did Mest and Wendy go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.54,0:19:02.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:05.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they forget the meeting place?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:06.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:07.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mest, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:08.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:12.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't meet him in Edolas, \Nso I don't know much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:16.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He joined during the two \Nyears I was away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.35,0:19:17.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.96,0:19:20.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like he's always been there...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.04,0:19:21.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not much of a presence, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:24.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia will go look for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:26.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a little worrying...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:28.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:31.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira, Lisanna, stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.68,0:19:35.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Juvia wanted to go cheer on Gray-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:42.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who are Men should \Nnot run from their enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:46.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Can't you just be quiet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:47.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:19:58.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:01.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:06.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing from before was a tactic \Nto throw Mira off her guard! An act!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:11.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure hope you didn't start thinking \Nthat I had a thing for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:13.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:16.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I am thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.74,0:20:19.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was one excellent under-handed \Nplan you thought up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:21.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call it under-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,0:20:24.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,People?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:30.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,People? On this island, people?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.59,0:20:37.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'd thought there wouldn't \Nbe anyone at this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:38.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:42.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Only members of our guild can enter here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.52,0:20:47.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guild? Oh... So this island \Nwas controlled by a guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:49.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:50.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:56.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't get close to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:57.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.41,0:21:00.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I'll leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:03.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:05.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:08.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.22,0:21:09.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we just leave him alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.55,0:21:14.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.51,0:21:17.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:22.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The predatory death...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:26.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.53,0:21:41.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.81,0:22:08.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.73,0:22:12.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.49,0:22:16.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.39,0:23:59.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's a little late, but why \Nare you blue if you're a cat, Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.19,0:24:01.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,More like, 100 episodes too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.14,0:24:03.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to know that, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.71,0:24:05.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure there's got to be a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.78,0:24:09.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An old passerby told me that everything \Nin this world has meaning, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.57,0:24:11.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An old passerby?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.44,0:24:13.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not someone important from long ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.92,0:24:16.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Black Wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.39,0:24:20.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because I'm like \Nthe bluebird of happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.48,0:24:22.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Happy, and I have wings and fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.98,0:24:24.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but you're a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.60,0:24:26.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
